        "generateUrl": "https://app.circleci.com/settings/user/tokens",
        "setup": "In the CircleCI app, open [User settings](https://app.circleci.com/settings/user), then [Personal API Tokens](https://app.circleci.com/settings/user/tokens), click **Create New Token**, give it a name, and click **Add API Token**. Copy the token when it is shown; CircleCI says you will not be able to view it again. The docs state personal API tokens are used to interact with CircleCI APIs v1 and v2, and the API developer guide says they are currently the only supported tokens on API v2.",
